<lb n="0676a22" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1168A [No. 1167]</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0676a23" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0676006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0676006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】，【原】麗本</note><app n="0676006"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0676006" type="rest" place="foot">【原】麗本</note>大乘八大曼拏羅經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0676a24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0676a25" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0676007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0676007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西【大】，宋西【明】</note><app n="0676007"><lem wit="【大】">西</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西</rdg></app>天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0676a26" ed="T"/>明教大師<note n="0676008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔臣〕－【明】</note><note n="0676008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臣【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0676008"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0676a27" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0676a2701">如是我聞。一時佛在補陀落迦山聖觀自在
<lb n="0676a28" ed="T"/>菩薩宮中。有無數百千俱胝那由他菩薩恭
<lb n="0676a29" ed="T"/>敬圍繞。爾時會中有一菩薩名寶藏月光。即
<pb n="0676b" xml:id="T20.1168A.0676b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0676b01" ed="T"/>從座起偏袒右肩。右膝著地合掌向佛。而白
<lb n="0676b02" ed="T"/>佛言世尊如來應供正等覺。今有所問願佛
<lb n="0676b03" ed="T"/>慈愍斷我疑惑。</p>
<lb n="0676b04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b0401">爾時世尊告寶藏月光菩薩摩訶薩言。汝今
<lb n="0676b05" ed="T"/>問我樂聞之法。是義云何當為汝說。時寶藏
<lb n="0676b06" ed="T"/>月光菩薩摩訶薩。聞佛語已而白佛言。世尊
<lb n="0676b07" ed="T"/>若有善男子善女人。欲作八大曼拏羅。云何
<lb n="0676b08" ed="T"/>受<note n="0676009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持＝特【元】</note><note n="0676009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持【大】，特【元】</note><app n="0676009"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">特</rdg></app>恭敬供養。佛言善哉善哉。若有善男子
<lb n="0676b09" ed="T"/>善女人。於此八大曼拏羅。依法受持恭敬供
<lb n="0676b10" ed="T"/>養。有大功德出生智慧利益無量。乃至三際
<lb n="0676b11" ed="T"/>眾生。皆得成就無等正智。善男子汝今諦聽。
<lb n="0676b12" ed="T"/>當為汝說此八大曼拏羅。具八大菩薩根本
<lb n="0676b13" ed="T"/>心大明。若常持誦恭敬供養。所有五逆重罪。
<lb n="0676b14" ed="T"/>一切諸惡悉皆除滅。而能成就無上勝義。大
<lb n="0676b15" ed="T"/>明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b1601" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>尾囉娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引<note n="0676010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【明】＊</note><note n="0676010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】＊，〔－〕【明】＊</note><app n="0676010"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0676b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b1701">此是佛心大明。安曼拏羅中心。誦此大明獻
<lb n="0676b18" ed="T"/>佛供養。</p>
<lb n="0676b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b1901">復次聖觀自在菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2001" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引</note>紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>賀鉢捺摩<note place="inline">二合</note>室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曳娑嚩
<lb n="0676b21" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0676011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【宋】【元】，〔引一〕－【明】</note><note n="0676011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引一【大】，〔－〕【明】，一【宋】【元】</note><app n="0676011"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0676b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2201">慈氏菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2301" cb:type="dharani">昧賀<note place="inline">引</note>囉尼娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引<app type="star" corresp="#0676010"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0676b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2401">虛空藏菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2501" cb:type="dharani">阿誐哩婆<note place="inline">二合引</note>野娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0676012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引一〕－【宋】【元】，引一＝一【明】</note><note n="0676012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】，一【明】</note><app n="0676012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0676b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2601">普賢菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2701" cb:type="dharani">莎紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>惹野娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引<note n="0676013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【三】</note><note n="0676013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0676013"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0676b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2801">金剛手菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676b2901" cb:type="dharani">俱尾囉娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引<app type="star" corresp="#0676010"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></p>
<pb n="0676c" xml:id="T20.1168A.0676c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0676c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676c0101">曼殊室哩菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676c0201" cb:type="dharani">室哩<note place="inline">二合引</note>暗囉伽娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引<note n="0676014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【三】</note><note n="0676014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0676014"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0676c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676c0301">除蓋障菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676c0401" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0676015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">儞＝付【元】</note><note n="0676015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儞【大】，付【元】</note><app n="0676015"><lem wit="【大】">儞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">付</rdg></app>娑囉嚩娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引一</note></p>
<lb n="0676c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676c0501">地藏菩薩心大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0676c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676c0601" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0676016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">叱＝摩【三】</note><note n="0676016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">叱【大】，摩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0676016"><lem wit="【大】">叱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">摩</rdg></app>賀<note place="inline">引</note>囉娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引<app type="star" corresp="#0676010"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0676c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0676c0701"><note n="0676017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如是＝爾時【三】</note><note n="0676017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如是【大】，爾時【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0676017"><lem wit="【大】">如是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">爾時</rdg></app>八大菩薩根本心大明。作如來曼拏羅。
<lb n="0676c08" ed="T"/>若有善男子善女人。於此曼拏羅依法受持。
<lb n="0676c09" ed="T"/><note n="0676018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">志＝至【明】</note><note n="0676018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">志【大】，至【明】</note><app n="0676018"><lem wit="【大】">志</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">至</rdg></app>心持誦根本大明。彼人速得成就阿耨多
<lb n="0676c10" ed="T"/>羅三藐三菩提。</p>
<lb n="0676c11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說大乘八大曼拏羅經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
